column2: SELECT prim.bestObjId, prim.mjd AS PrimMJD, z, velDisp FROM SpecObjAll prim  JOIN SpecObjAll other ON prim.bestObjId = other.bestObjId  JOIN platex AS plate ON other.plate = plate.plate AND other.mjd = plate.mjd WHERE other.bestObjId > #  AND prim.sciencePrimary = #  AND other.sciencePrimary = #  AND prim.z > # ORDER BY prim.bestObjId
